{"tid":2405467,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨政府澄清：港台跟隨「一國一制」停播BBC屬編採自主 黨政府一如既往堅持「一國兩制」方針","createTime":"2021-02-12T11:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T11:58:29.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2bc9ff026e7d7b85cb7d0708e692337487d88b08","tid":2405467,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T11:20:27.000Z","msg":"港台停播BBC頻道及節目 通訊局：屬編輯決定<br />\n<br />\n國家廣電總局禁止英國廣播公司BBC世界新聞台，在中國境內落地，批評BBC報道違反「真實和公正」的要求，損害中國利益。香港電台發言人表示，根據國家廣電總局決定，港台今晚11時開始，不再轉播BBC國際頻道，及《BBC時事一週》節目。<br />\n<br />\n通訊局回覆查詢時表示，本地持牌廣播機構，或者香港電台，是否轉播某個外國頻道的電視節目，屬於編輯決定，通訊局並無就此設限。<br />\n<br />\n對於會否禁止BBC記者出席政府記者會，政府發言人表示，香港享有新聞自由，特區政府亦一直對各國媒體和記者在港從事採訪工作提供便利，這項政策符合《基本法》和「一國兩制」方針。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2378932\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2378932&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FCpZd1NrJsyKidS%2BVLva3MM%3D&h=8338acb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2378932</a>"},{"pid":"4b1897bd0e18530fe2b376b5847c8b55c0759d60","tid":2405467,"uid":387461,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T11:21:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">係囉我都覺</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"47c51e5b9bda48c584228a15f9d2f4afcc8aa8de","tid":2405467,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T11:22:05.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">  一國一制  </span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></p>"},{"pid":"5cc2768934c1a02aa191d7ada33a8a8ac4789337","tid":2405467,"uid":37874,"